
'''''Aki na Ukwa''''' ni filimi yakorewe muri Nigeriya muri 2002 iyobowe na Amayo Uzo Philips. Muri filime [[Osita Iheme|hagaragaramo Osita Iheme]] na [[Chinedu Ikedieze]] . Filime yatangije umwuga wo gukinana ari abakinnyi bombi Osita na Chinedu kandi iyi film yaranze ubufatanye bwabo bwa mbere.    Iyi filime yashimiwe cyane ko yafunguye ibitekerezo byiza kandi iyi filime yafashwe nka imwe muri filime nziza kurusha izindi zose muri sinema yo muri Nijeriya ahanini hagamijwe kumenyekanisha Osita Iheme na Chinedu Ikedieze mu nshingano zabo bakina abiyita  ba PawPaw na Aki. .  <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201802190082.html</ref> Aba bombi bahagurukiye kuba ibyamamare maze bahinduka ijuru ryose muri Nijeriya kubera imikorere yabo muri filime kuva yasohoka.   Kuva icyo gihe, aba bombi bakinnye hamwe muri firime nyinshi mu nshingano zabo.   Chukwuka Emelionwu wari uwatunganije iyi filime yashimiwe kuba yararemye abantu baranga "Aki" na "PawPaw". 

== Inyandiko ==
Abavandimwe babiri bateza akaduruvayo mu rugo rwabo, mu ishuri ryabo ndetse no mu mudugudu wabo wose. 

